{"cells":[{"cell_type":"code","source":["import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n","import numpy as np\n","\n","# Sample data - generating random data points using normal distribution\n","np.random.seed(0)\n","x = np.random.randn(1000)\n","y = np.random.randn(1000)\n","colors = np.random.randint(10, 101, size=1000)\n","sizes = np.random.randint(10, 101, size=1000)\n","\n","# Scatter plot with multiple customizations\n","plt.scatter(x, y, c=colors, cmap=\"viridis\", s=sizes, marker='o', alpha=0.5)\n","plt.xlabel('X')\n","plt.ylabel('Y')\n","plt.title('Scatter Plot with Matplotlib')\n","plt.show()"],"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["<module 'matplotlib.pyplot' from '/lib/python3.12/site-packages/matplotlib/pyplot.py'>"],"text/html":["<img src=\"data:image/png;charset=utf-8;base64,\"  style=\"height:400px;object-fit:contain\" />"]},"metadata":{}}],"metadata":{"fiddle":{"running":false,"focus":false,"success":true}},"id":"6a11b58e-dc4a-434b-98c7-98b31358c186"}],"metadata":{"kernelspec":{"name":"pyodide","display_name":"Python","language":"python","ext":"py"}},"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":5,"id":"c23205e6-e2e3-4571-b5fb-e1ca1e01a40d"}
